{"tid":2511184,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港新加坡旅遊氣泡的延伸推斷, 將來要出境需打左疫苗","createTime":"2021-04-30T16:53:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T10:37:49.000Z","uid":76310,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"959b63ababa4e732958aa9ff417efb1e02d4d05a","tid":2511184,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T16:53:39.000Z","msg":"香港新加坡旅遊氣泡的延伸推斷<br />\n當日我還以為是馬騮国要求香港人打左疫苗才可以到馬騮国<br />\n本身還以為是不平等<br />\n但原來一切都是777的意思<br />\n<br />\n香港居民須在完成接種兩劑 2019 冠狀病毒病疫苗最少 14 天後，方可乘搭專屬航班由香港出發前往新加坡<br />\n就是說, 要出境, 就需要打疫苗<br />\n<br />\n但相信這只是初步試驗<br />\n是一個先行大型實踐的試驗場<br />\n將來8月後, 鎖港條例一過<br />\n依治限制你出境<br />\n<br />\n將來要出境香港需打左疫苗<br />\n無打疫苗無得出境"},{"pid":"d928939dfdc54a5af4e5f1f164120a8ea85ce2d3","tid":2511184,"uid":260654,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T18:44:39.000Z","msg":"你知我知個單眼佬都知.gif"},{"pid":"51479c72a909334bebe0a8305a75dde919ba4390","tid":2511184,"uid":107567,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T23:52:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebdae3307f193c7f982b18e57163cf87217cc6a","tid":2511184,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:11:35.000Z","msg":"都係嗰句，唔好打中文啦，中文嚟自官話，係蝗文嚟"},{"pid":"c44d66a46058bba6b06b260d2a97cc6e5beb2100","tid":2511184,"uid":32722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"51479c72a909334bebe0a8305a75dde919ba4390","tid":2511184,"uid":107567,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T23:52:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:45:41.000Z","msg":"到時累撚埋個醫生除牌"},{"pid":"d9f716f66a20b8ee3e979e0650ea488f7fb0ad50","tid":2511184,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T09:56:15.000Z","msg":"既然無香港人打<br />\n不如將所有BNT疫苗送晒比印度國, 用左佢, 唔好浪費<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412f3c7db74f72342fd2bfde8dd9873342f4687f","tid":2511184,"uid":240670,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T10:37:49.000Z","msg":"一早預左<br />\n<br />\n港共遲早會強制出境要先打齊2劑毒針<br />\n打唔死就用有新毒針防範變種中國肺炎<br />\n打夠4劑先比你出境<br />\n<br />\n打毒針唔死?<br />\n打多幾劑囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一來清到貨<br />\n二來打撚死你無得走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}